'''印度超級聯賽'''（Indian Super League），因贊助關係，官方名字為Hero印度超級聯賽，是[[印度|印度]]的職業足球聯賽。與[[印度足球甲级联赛|印度足球甲级联赛]]同為印度頂級聯賽。但他們是以八支加盟球隊所組成的<ref name="Bloomberg Sachin">{{cite web|last1=Katakey|first1=Rakteem|title=Tendulkar Buys Team as Cricket-Mad India Tests Soccer League|url=http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2014-04-14/tendulkar-buys-soccer-team-as-cricket-mad-india-tests-new-league.html|website=Bloomberg|accessdate=21 July 2014|archive-date=2014-08-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140818082034/http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2014-04-14/tendulkar-buys-soccer-team-as-cricket-mad-india-tests-new-league.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。聯賽由10月-12月舉行，並會由季後賽決定冠軍誰屬<ref>{{cite web|last1=Mergulhao|first1=Marcus|title=ISL postponed again, by 3 weeks|url=http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/sports/football/indian-super-league/top-stories/ISL-postponed-again-by-3-weeks/articleshow/39144547.cms|website=Times of India|accessdate=28 July 2014|archive-date=2019-03-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190328031715/https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com//sports/football/indian-super-league/top-stories/ISL-postponed-again-by-3-weeks/articleshow/39144547.cms|dead-url=no}}</ref>。除此之外，印超还设有[[选秀|选秀]]。

印超聯於2013年成立，希望令足球成為印度的頂級活動，並將印度足球推廣全球<ref name=Founded>{{cite web|title=RELIANCE, IMG WORLDWIDE AND STAR INDIA, LAUNCH `INDIAN SUPER LEAGUE' FOR FOOTBALL|url=http://img.com/news/news/2013/october/reliance,-img-worldwide-and-star-india,-launch-%60in.aspx|website=IMG|accessdate=21 July 2014|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141008194259/http://img.com/news/news/2013/october/reliance%2C-img-worldwide-and-star-india%2C-launch-%60in.aspx|archivedate=2014年10月8日}}</ref>。聯賽與[[印度超級木球聯賽|印度超級木球聯賽]]和[[美職聯|美職聯]]有合作關係<ref name=MLSstyle>{{cite web|last=Bali|first=Rahul|title=IMG-Reliance keen to start an eight team franchisee competition, I-League likely to follow the MLS|url=http://www.goal.com/en-india/news/136/india/2012/07/19/3250992/img-reliance-keen-to-start-an-eight-team-franchisee|work=Goal.com|accessdate=20 October 2013|archive-date=2015-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924144727/http://www.goal.com/en-india/news/136/india/2012/07/19/3250992/img-reliance-keen-to-start-an-eight-team-franchisee|dead-url=no}}</ref>。與主流聯賽不同，印超聯沒有[[升降班制度|升降班制度]]，反之，他們是有八支特許經營球隊所組成的<ref name=MLSstyle/>。

首屆賽事於2014年10月12日星期日舉行，並於同年12月20日完結<ref>{{cite web|last1=Bali|first1=Rahul|title=ISL to kick-off on October 12|url=http://www.goal.com/en-india/news/7083/isl/2014/07/26/4985448/isl-to-kick-off-on-october-12|website=Goal.com|accessdate=3 August 2014|archive-date=2020-09-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200922065118/https://www.goal.com/en-india/news/7083/isl/2014/07/26/4985448/isl-to-kick-off-on-october-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[加爾各答體育會|加爾各答體育會]]擊敗[[喀拉拉爆破手|喀拉拉爆破手]]而取得首屆冠軍，而首屆聯賽入座率則是印度所有聯賽排名第四<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.indiansuperleague.com/matchcentre/2014122013849-kerala-blasters-fc-vs-atletico-de-kolkata|title=Match Report|work=Indian Super league|accessdate=20 December 2014|archive-date=2014-12-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141220172247/http://www.indiansuperleague.com/matchcentre/2014122013849-kerala-blasters-fc-vs-atletico-de-kolkata|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

